title: Match History Question
body: Sorry, this is probably a really stupid question, but what do the three numbers represent in your match history? eg. 16/9/5

replies.body:
There are many numbers that represent many different things, and there are two forms of match history.

That number right there, however, looks like a kills/deaths/assists counter. Basically, for whichever summoner that was, they got sixteen kills, died nine times, and helped their allies kill an enemy five times.

If you'd like more clarity, capture a screenshot and circle the exact numbers, so that we can be one-hundred percent sure of this.
